Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:02.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.44,0:00:04.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's time for Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.91,0:00:06.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to gather all the shards\nof the Sacred Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.08,0:00:08.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I'll destroy Naraku\nwith my Tetsusaiga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:10.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In our search for clues to\NNaraku's whereabouts,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:13.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}we head towards the sacred\nland of Mt. Hakurei.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.75,0:00:17.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Blocking our way is Bankotsu,\nthe leader of the Band of Seven,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:18.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}who finally makes himself\nknown to us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.02,0:00:20.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku, Sango, Shippo and Kirara...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.69,0:00:21.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}travel back in time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:22.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To a Feudal Fairytale...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.13,0:00:23.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:20.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's {\i1}see....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:28.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Agh! No good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:33.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}know....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:37.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wash your {\i1}face....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:38.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:40.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:41.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:45.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:46.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:55.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bankotsu....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:55.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:02:57.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I brought your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.09,0:03:02.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bankotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:04.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:15.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:17.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:18.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:20.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But {\i1}say....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:21.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Big {\i1}Brother....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:24.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kyokotsu and Mukotsu {\i1}were....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:26.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't be helped\nif they were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:27.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You knew?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:28.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But {\i1}Renkotsu....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:29.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:32.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're smart.\NSo you can write.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:33.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:35.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:37.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's {\i1}see....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:39.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"We're coming to\nsettle old scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:43.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Wash your {\i1}face....{\i0}\NI mean neck, and wait."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:44.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's payback time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:48.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NThat castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:50.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:51.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:55.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The bastards in that castle\nchopped our heads off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:03.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That last battle was\na lot of fun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:06.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was such a stupid lord.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:10.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hope this fight is fun, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:12.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Big Brother, what do you think?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:13.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will it be fun?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:15.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, I think it will be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look, there it is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:25.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:27.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:29.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The general of the samurai\nof this castle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:33.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? Isn't the lord himself\ngonna appear?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:36.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want you to attack\nthe eastern lands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:38.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}An advance guard?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:42.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you're the rumored Band of Seven,\nit should be easy work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:43.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as the money is right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:47.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our lord has instructed me to\npay whatever you demand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:49.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, we'll accept.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:55.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank goodness other daimyo lords\nhadn't defeated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:58.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah. My companion is there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:00.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You {\i1}mean....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:01.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:03.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They had some nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Big Brother. Will this do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:08.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:12.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:16.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this to that castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:18.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hand it to the clan lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:19.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.26,0:05:21.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're a ninja, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:23.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:25.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:25.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:28.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Never mind, I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:34.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be careful, Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:43.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:46.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Didn't you want to eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:51.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Was I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:00.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:01.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:03.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What about preparations\nto attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:06.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why'd you think I sent that letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:10.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to take my time and\nwatch those guys squirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:11.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Humph....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:15.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll let them keep my companion\na while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:27.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's just as Kikyo said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:31.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:35.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This Mt. Hakurei\nis so serene.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:38.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kirara?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:41.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:43.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:47.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, what does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:49.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They've been exposed to\nthe {\i1}ki{\i0} of the Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.15,0:06:53.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After all, Shippo and Kirara\nare real demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:56.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even half-demon Inuyasha\nmust feel it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:04.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:06.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:09.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's probably to protect\nthis sacred place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:13.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In fact, it's a powerful barrier
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:16.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,strong enough to instantly purify\nevil and demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:19.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm human,\nand even for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:22.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,this immaculate purity\nis uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:25.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?\NWe're fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:25.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe you're {\i1}impure....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:29.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whaa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:33.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:36.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! Don't do that! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please stop!\NStop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:47.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You ARE impure!\NAnd you're a monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:52.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now it's clear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:54.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought that, {\i1}perhaps....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:57.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku was taking advantage of\nthis barrier to hide himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:08:00.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:02.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's a mass of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:07.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He takes one step into the mountain\nand he'll be purified immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:08.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:11.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no way Naraku\ncould survive in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:14.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The barrier of Mt. Hakurei\nis amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:16.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:19.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:21.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, what'll we do\nfrom now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:22.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:26.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's whereabouts.\NHe's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:28.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Band of Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:30.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll look for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:34.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Without a doubt, Naraku\nis connected to them somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:36.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll capture them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:39.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and make them confess\nwhere Naraku is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:43.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then, let's descend\nthis mountain quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:45.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo and Kirara\nseem to be in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:47.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:50.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0} He's the one\nwho's in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:53.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He {\i1}really{\i0} must be impure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:01.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:03.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:04.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.22,0:09:08.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If young ones like you\nwander around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.89,0:09:10.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the men from the castle\nwill capture you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:12.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:16.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The young ones in this area\nwere all forcibly taken away to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.69,0:09:19.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Regardless of if they were\njust traveling through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is there a big battle coming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:22.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:26.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it seems a warning was\nsent to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:27.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Warning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:30.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That the castle treasure\nwould be seized.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:32.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Castle treasure?\NLike what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:34.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:38.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In any case, you'd better\nhide out somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:40.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:41.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:43.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The general from the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:47.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You there!\NIdentify yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:50.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're just travelers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:52.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't take me for a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:53.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:57.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demons wandering in\nour borders in broad daylight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:10:00.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You got a problem with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:05.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're lucky this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:08.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But there won't be a second chance.\NLeave our fief immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.41,0:10:10.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:12.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:14.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:18.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you know\nabout the Band of Seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:19.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Band of Seven?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:23.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old man, you know something\nabout them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:28.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At one time, the Band of Seven were\nmercenaries who wreaked havoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:30.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's old news!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:33.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The one who killed the\NBand of Seven
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:35.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is rumored to be that\nsamurai general.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:36.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:38.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:40.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That one is a devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:42.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:44.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Should we go and\ntalk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:45.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Better not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:48.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you approach the castle,\nyou'll only get in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:52.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:01.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look! There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:05.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Makes me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:06.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You got that right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:10.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn, we really got it\nthat time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:17.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Take that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:42.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was easy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.17,0:11:43.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Such a disappointment!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:46.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No kidding.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:47.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He may be a daimyo,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:50.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but he's no match\nfor the Band of Seven!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:51.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Big Brother...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:55.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't it time we find a castle\nto lord over?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:59.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean, you could even\nbecome Shogun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:02.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That'll be a pain!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:07.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you want to?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:10.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Become a daimyo lord\nor Shogun?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:11.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:14.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd never overstep you,\NBig Brother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.34,0:12:16.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you want, I'll help you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.91,0:12:20.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who knows how many men\nwe'll have to kill first.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:22.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Makes me excited!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:26.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Me, too!\NWhat a turn-on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.92,0:12:30.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can kill until we're bored,\nand there'll still be more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:39.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hah! Haven't learned\ntheir lesson yet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:42.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's go kill some more!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:44.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay! Let's get to work!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:46.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:54.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey! I thought we were\nthe advance guard!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:57.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Band of Seven\nhas gotten too notorious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:12:59.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Changed your mind\nabout paying us?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:02.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You kill too much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:04.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whether you are friend orfoe,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.79,0:13:08.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the daimyo lords believe\nthe Band of Seven are too strong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:10.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Brother!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:11.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Big Brother!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.40,0:13:14.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And you think you can\ndefeat us?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is nowhere you can escape.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:19.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Consider every daimyo\nin the surrounding region your enemy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:21.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:27.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Big Brother!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:28.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Run!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:43.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are too dangerous\neven in this age of wars!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:45.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:51.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Before I died the first time,\NI killed 999 men.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:54.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now I can make it a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:57.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't fail, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:13:59.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If it's a real fight,\nwe won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:02.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:10.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder when we'll be able\nto return to the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:12.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wanna go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:12.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.02,0:14:13.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get back to your positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:16.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:19.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My {\i1}lord....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:21.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Reinforcements will\narrive shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.93,0:14:24.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've gathered the villagers\nto take up arms
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.54,0:14:26.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and the castle is completely secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:29.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! You're overreacting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:31.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:32.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:35.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop!\NWho are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:36.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But my {\i1}lord....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:40.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Calamities thought to be the work\nof the specters of the Band of Seven
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:42.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,have caused panic\nin various regions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:46.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Banryu,\nour clan's treasured {\i1}halberd....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:47.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:51.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm here to take back\nmy companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:52.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:54.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:55.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:15:01.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the proof of our killing of\NBankotsu, the leader of the Band of Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:05.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If he attacks again,\nwe'll just beat {\i1}him....{\i0} Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:06.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:13.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:15.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not allow them to enter\nthe castle grounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.32,0:15:22.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:30.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:34.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:35.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:38.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They will not attack\nany further.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:41.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:42.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you read the letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:44.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:46.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are the guards?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:48.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.15,0:15:51.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't think they'll be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:53.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}T-That's....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:55.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:57.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:16:01.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You desire this....halberd, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:03.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, there's my Banryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:06.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here. You can have it {\i1}back....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:16.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?! That huge halberd required\nthree men to carry it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:18.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That young brat is holding\nit in one hand!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:25.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow! It's so shiny!\NYou polished it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:28.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:30.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if you are a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:31.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you serve me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:33.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:35.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall make you a vassal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:37.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And together in this feudal age,\nwe {\i1}shall....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:40.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey you! Did you read the\nletter carefully?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:42.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:44.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:45.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:49.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Didn't it say to "wash your neck\nand wait"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.68,0:16:50.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:53.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll {\i1}be....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:54.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Number 1000!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:01.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:02.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:03.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:08.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Reinforcements have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:10.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, shall we live it up\nsome more?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:12.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You guys, move aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:15.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You got it back, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:18.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This will be a good warm-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:19.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:22.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:26.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:28.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:30.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:31.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What did you do\nto our lord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:33.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His {\i1}head....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:34.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Head?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.89,0:17:37.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Our heads were chopped off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:39.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So we just paid him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:41.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:43.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you wash your neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:47.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.31,0:17:56.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hah! This feels better than\nwhen I was alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:05.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! I sense\na Sacred Jewel shard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:07.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not only that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:09.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I smell gunpowder and\nlots of blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:11.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Band of Seven are up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:28.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A slaughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:31.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:34.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jakotsu, this is your doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:39.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Couldn't you keep one woman\nalive to pour {\i1}sake?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:42.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forget that, Bankotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:45.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This isn't the time to be\ndrinking {\i1}sake!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:49.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't wait to see Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:51.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be so rash, Jakotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:53.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha has a keen\nsense of smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:56.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, we just have to wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:59.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He'll come following the\nscent of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:03.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really? I guess we wait then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:05.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still....{\i0} Big {\i1}Brother....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:06.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:08.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Doesn't Naraku worry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:09.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:11.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did he bring us back\nfrom the dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:16.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He wanted us to get rid of\nthose {\i1}pests....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:18.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,like Inuyasha and Koga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:20.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Big {\i1}Brother....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:22.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the only one who's\nmet Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.27,0:19:26.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can you tell us more about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:29.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen {\i1}Renkotsu....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:31.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've been resurrected.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:34.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And we can wreak havoc\njust like old times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:36.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.38,0:19:37.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:41.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once he makes up his mind,\NBig Brother never changes it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:47.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wish Inuyasha would come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:50.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:53.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A whirlwind!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:00.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must be the Band of Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:02.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Yo, Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.94,0:20:05.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So the wolf comes\nbefore the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:07.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quit acting so smug!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:11.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know that you're in cahoots\nwith Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:12.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me where Naraku is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:17.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gee, this Naraku has made enemies\nof a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:19.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:24.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Makes me wonder.\NCan he be trusted?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:26.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:29.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the only one who's\nmet him, Bankotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:31.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you try to keep it {\i1}secret....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:33.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.57,0:20:39.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right! We still have\na match to finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.74,0:20:41.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.71,0:20:43.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've already seen through {\i1}your....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.11,0:20:45.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,weird sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:50.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He avoided it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:55.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, you're pretty nimble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:58.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Must be the Shikon Jewel shards\nin your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:00.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:03.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku asked {\i1}me....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:05.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to take them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:09.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why that...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:18.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.15,0:21:20.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:22.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This guy isn't like the rest of them...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.52,0:21:25.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone!\NDon't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.81,0:21:43.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.97,0:21:45.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Move it, you wimpy wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.61,0:21:50.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.42,0:21:56.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I found {\i1}you....{\i0} Band of Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.10,0:23:48.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to avenge the deaths\nof Mukotsu and Kyokotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.10,0:23:50.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're the leader of\nthe Band of Seven?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.27,0:23:51.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be careful, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.47,0:23:54.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Bankotsu has three\NSacred Jewel shards around his neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.64,0:23:56.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you want to know\NNaraku's hideout,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.51,0:23:57.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,ask my Banryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.17,0:23:59.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In the midst of the vicious\nattack by the Band of Seven,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:01.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku makes his appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.88,0:24:04.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sesshomaru?!\NKill him, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.35,0:24:09.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\NThe Big Clash:\NBanryu versus the Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.19,0:24:12.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Water and the smell of {\i1}flowers....{\i0}\NWhat do they mean?!
